-- Berkshire’s MiTek Buys Kova in Residential Construction Wager
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2013-10-10T19:06:12Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-10-10/berkshire-s-mitek-buys-kova-in-residential-construction-wager.html
MiTek Industries, the unit at  Warren Buffett ’s Berkshire Hathaway Inc. that provides software and
structural systems for buildings, acquired Kova Solutions to
expand sales in the residential construction market.  Jouko Vakiparta will remain the leader of Kova, according
to a Business Wire statement today from Chesterfield, Missouri-based MiTek that didn’t disclose terms.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
